7DegJ9fm82NfKQ/viewform" data-lynx-mode="async" data-lynx-uri="https://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSfzzDeU1ioi1HUl_BQhaBrF8LuxPjJdoWN97DegJ9fm82NfKQ%2Fviewform&amp;h=ATMk5nEjEPt8-BGoT1IjC6VmumG-XqIhr4kJkaSawo-GnVFToUsM049zVmiqCJmWCVkobAdvKAK0-XmxYnP4DYlYL3lzj98z_LA1HlBL5Vv8RJYB4RA9X5R8n-ft7su4SSz30J3qCUOfKyUqBnnIfDus2wF71dkdfpQPVopQn7Qy6TjH">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfzzDeU1ioi1HUl_BQhaBrF8LuxPjJdoWN97DegJ9fm82NfKQ/viewform</a>', '9月7日（木）ミートアップ・イベント「Tsumugu Vol.2」を開催します！', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1074-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-08-24 11:49:58', '2017-08-24 02:49:58', '', 1074, 'http://latest-smc-corporate/1085', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
